model

Class Module

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Module

  • public class Module
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines a sort of beans objects which contain all the parsed information from a module of a CafeOBJ file and will be used to retrieve the information in order to create the JML contract for that class
    Author:
    nikos
